OL,7,FAt day two of the Covid Inquiry in
OL,8,FBelfast, the former head of the Civil
OL,9,FService has defended not activating
OL,10,Fcontingency planning earlier at the
OL,11,Fstart of the Covid-19 pandemic.
OL,13,FSir David Sterling also said how
OL,14,Frelations between senior politicians
OL,15,F"soured" following Sinn Fein's
OL,16,Fattendance at the funeral of former
OL,17,FIRA leader, Bobby Storey.
