OL,7,FThere was a "discernible chill"
OL,8,Fbetween Northern Ireland's First
OL,9,FMinister Arlene Foster and deputy
OL,10,FFirst Minister Michelle O'Neill
OL,11,Ffollowing the funeral of IRA veteran
OL,12,FBobby Storey, the Covid-19 Inquiry has
OL,13,Fheard.
OL,15,FMs O'Neill attended the large-scale
OL,16,Ffuneral in west Belfast for Mr Storey
OL,17,Fin June 2020 despite lockdown
OL,18,Frestrictions on public gatherings.
