OL,7,FThe then head of the Northern Ireland
OL,8,FCivil Service, Sir David Sterling,
OL,9,Fsaid her attendance affected relations
OL,10,Fat the Stormont Executive.
OL,12,FThis included Ms Foster and Ms O'Neill
OL,13,Fstopping their then daily joint press
OL,14,Fconferences on Covid-19.
OL,16,FAppearing at the UK-wide Covid-19
OL,17,FInquiry sitting in Belfast, Sir David
OL,18,Fsaid he would not comment on the issue
OL,19,Fitself but said it did cause divisions.
OL,1,Wj5k7j5                          G4/39
