OL,7,F"The atmosphere in the Executive was
OL,8,Fdifficult after that. One of the most
OL,9,Fimmediate practical implications was
OL,10,Fthat the joint press conferences which
OL,11,Ftook place most afternoons by the
OL,12,FFirst Minister and deputy First
OL,13,FMinister stopped, and that was
OL,14,Fsignificant because the feedback we
OL,15,Fgot from the start from attitude
OL,16,Fsurveys etc was that the community
OL,17,Ffound those press conferences very
OL,18,Fhelpful, very reassuring, and it was a
OL,19,Fvery visible manifestation of
OL,20,Fministers working together, and the
OL,21,Fabsence of that I think did reduce
OL,22,Fpublic confidence for a period of
OL,23,Ftime," he said.
