OL,7,FPressed by Clair Dobbin, lead counsel
OL,8,Fto the inquiry, Sir David added: "It
OL,9,Fwasn't helpful... generally it's just
OL,10,Fharder to do business whenever the
OL,11,Frelationship is not as it should be."
OL,13,FOn Tuesday during opening statements,
OL,14,Fthe inquiry heard that in March 2020,
OL,15,FSir David sent a Whatsapp messages
OL,16,Fcriticising political division at
OL,17,FStormont as ministers discussed
OL,18,Flockdown measures.
