OL,7,FIn one message on March 17, he
OL,8,Fdescribed an Executive meeting the
OL,9,Fprevious day as "excruciating", adding
OL,10,F"no leadership on display at all".
OL,12,FOn Wednesday, Sir David was asked
OL,13,Fabout the message by Ms Dobbin.
OL,15,FHe said he wanted to clarify that
OL,16,Fmessage came during what he said "was
OL,17,Fprobably the most difficult two or
OL,18,Fthree days that I experienced during
OL,19,Fthe first wave".
