OL,7,FSir David added: "I think it's just
OL,8,Frecognising our context where we have
OL,9,Ffive parties in an enforced coalition,
OL,10,Fvery different ideologies, very
OL,11,Fdifferent aspirations for this place,
OL,12,Fhaving to work together, but I think
OL,13,Fit's important to recognise that on
OL,14,Fall the big issues they eventually did
OL,15,Freach decisions.
OL,17,F"It was painstaking, it was difficult
OL,18,Fat times but decisions were taken."
