OL,7,FNorthern Ireland's commissioner for
OL,8,Folder people has blasted as "reckless"
OL,9,Fcases during the pandemic where people
OL,10,Fwere discharged to care homes without
OL,11,Fbeing tested for Covid-19.
OL,13,FEddie Lynch said it was a "serious
OL,14,Fconcern" among both the families of
OL,15,Fpatients and care providers.
