OL,7,FHe also called for better
OL,8,Funderstanding surrounding restrictions
OL,9,Fon families visiting their loved ones
OL,10,Fin care homes at points during the
OL,11,Fpandemic, describing the situation as
OL,12,F"devastating".
OL,14,FMr Lynch made his comments while
OL,15,Fgiving evidence to the second day of
OL,16,Fthe UK-wide Covid-19 Inquiry's sitting
OL,17,Fin Belfast.
OL,19,FHe described the coronavirus pandemic
OL,20,Fas a "steep learning curve".
