OL,7,FThe commissioner said his office
OL,8,Freceived a lot of contact in the early
OL,9,Fstages of the pandemic around patients
OL,10,Fbeing discharged to care homes without
OL,11,Fa Covid-19 test.
OL,13,F"It did come to my attention several
OL,14,Ftimes about the hospitals being
OL,15,Fcleared out to make space for a
OL,16,Fpossible surge of Covid patients, and
OL,17,Fpart of that seemed to be discharging
OL,18,Fpeople into care homes where they
OL,19,Fcould," he said.
OL,26,@uD@AOU{D@GO]
