OL,7,F"I was very concerned, as so were the
OL,8,Fcare home providers, that those people
OL,9,Fwere put into those settings without
OL,10,Ftesting.
OL,12,F"I think it was very clear cut that
OL,13,Fthe policy of discharging people
OL,14,Fwithout testing into those settings
OL,15,Fwas a potentially disastrous one. I
OL,16,Fthink it was quite reckless a decision
OL,17,Fto take to allow that to happen."
