OL,7,FMr Lynch also said he would like an
OL,8,Foutcome of the inquiry to be looking
OL,9,Fat how care homes could be protected
OL,10,Fin the event of something similar
OL,11,Fhappening again, given the
OL,12,F"devastating" impact of people not
OL,13,Fbeing able to visit their loved ones.
OL,15,F"I think that issue of human contact
OL,16,Fand visiting would have to be
OL,17,Fsomething that a future pandemic needs
