OL,7,FHe said the Department of Health took
OL,8,Fa "reactive response" to planning and
OL,9,Fprotecting people during the pandemic,
OL,10,Fbut that it exposed a "dividing line"
OL,11,Fbetween the health service and social
OL,12,Fcare sector.
OL,14,F"There was clearly a focus on
OL,15,Fprotecting the NHS, the concern was
OL,16,Fclearly about hospital capacity, but
OL,17,Fas a result of that we saw a lot of
OL,18,Fthe care home and social care sector
OL,19,Freally struggle," he said.
