OL,7,FThe hearings in Belfast will run for
OL,8,Fthree weeks and are designed to
OL,9,Fprovide an opportunity to look in
OL,10,Fdepth at the decisions taken in
OL,11,FNorthern Ireland.
OL,13,FThis module will investigate the
OL,14,Finitial response, central government
OL,15,Fdecision making, political and civil
OL,16,Fservice performance as well as the
OL,17,Feffectiveness of relationships with
OL,18,Fgovernments in the devolved
OL,19,Fadministrations and local and
OL,20,Fvoluntary sectors.
