OL,7,FWorkers in processing plants were
OL,8,Fparticularly at risk during the
OL,9,Fpandemic, a senior trade union
OL,10,Fofficial has said.
OL,12,FGerry Murphy, from the Irish Congress
OL,13,Fof Trade Unions (ICTU), started his
OL,14,Fevidence to the Covid-19 Inquiry
OL,15,Fsitting in Belfast by remembering the
OL,16,F400 people of working age in Northern
OL,17,FIreland who died during the pandemic.
