OL,7,FHe said he hopes the work of the
OL,8,Finquiry as a whole "will aid the
OL,9,Fcreation of a set of circumstances
OL,10,Fwhere such a situation will never
OL,11,Farise again".
OL,13,FThe inquiry heard that some 30,000
OL,14,Fworkers in Northern Ireland are
OL,15,Femployed through agencies, with a
OL,16,Flarge proportion of these during the
OL,17,Fpandemic working in agriculture and
OL,18,Fthe food processing sector.
