OL,7,FIt also heard that the highest
OL,8,Fproportion of deaths among people of
OL,9,Fworking age in the region were among
OL,10,Fworkers in processing plants and
OL,11,Fmachine operatives.
OL,13,F"13.4% of that 400 who lost their
OL,14,Flives were in that sector," Mr Murphy
OL,15,Ftold the inquiry.
