OL,7,FMr Murphy said following the death of
OL,8,Fa worker at a processing plant, a
OL,9,Fsenior Unite official wrote to the
OL,10,Fthen-first minister Dame Arlene Foster
OL,11,Fand Michelle O'Neill raising concern
OL,12,Fthat there should have been mass Covid
OL,13,Ftesting in that sector.
OL,15,F"That never happened. There should
OL,16,Fhave been more unannounced
OL,17,Finspections. That didn't happen
OL,18,Feither," he said.
