OL,7,F"Unite the Union felt, and we shared
OL,8,Fthis view up to a point as well, that
OL,9,Fthere was some wilful disregarding of
OL,10,Fthe advice on the part of some of the
OL,11,Femployers.
OL,13,F"Those working in processing plants
OL,14,Fwere particularly at risk, as were
OL,15,Fthose who were in front-facing
OL,16,Foccupations such as retail ` that was
OL,17,Fthe other big proportion of those 400
OL,18,Flives that were lost."
