OL,7,FMr Murphy was also asked about an
OL,8,Fengagement forum that the trade unions
OL,9,Fhad taken part in during the early
OL,10,Fpart of the pandemic.
OL,12,FHe said it did good work initially,
OL,13,Fidentifying the list of key workers
OL,14,Fand essential sectors, but later in
OL,15,F2020 it had ceased to function
OL,16,Feffectively and had effectively ended
OL,17,Fby 2021.
OL,19,FHe suggested that political leaders be
OL,20,Fasked why the work of the forum did
OL,21,Fnot continue.
