OL,7,FActivating emergency response to Covid
OL,8,Fin NI few days earlier 'probably
OL,9,Fprudent'
OL,11,FThe former head of Northern Ireland's
OL,12,FCivil Service has said it "probably
OL,13,Fwould have been prudent" to have
OL,14,Festablished the emergency response to
OL,15,Fthe coronavirus pandemic days earlier.
OL,17,FThe UK government initiated COBR in
OL,18,FJanuary 2020, but Stormont did not
OL,19,Factivate the Northern Ireland Central
OL,20,FCrisis Management Arrangements
OL,21,F(NICCMA) until March.
