OL,7,FThe first case of Covid-19 was
OL,8,Fconfirmed in Northern Ireland on
OL,9,FFebruary 27, while the first death
OL,10,Fwith the virus was recorded on March
OL,11,F19.
OL,13,FGiving evidence to the Covid-19
OL,14,FInquiry sitting in Belfast on
OL,15,FWednesday, then head of the Northern
OL,16,FIreland Civil Service Sir David
OL,17,FSterling said in his view you did not
OL,18,Factivate the NICCMA until you had
OL,19,Fmoved out of the prepare phase.
