OL,7,FHe said they were in daily contact
OL,8,Fwith the Department of Health and
OL,9,Fattending COBR meetings.
OL,11,F"I was always very clear that at any
OL,12,Fpoint in time they asked us to
OL,13,Factivate NICCMA, and by that I mean
OL,14,Festablish the Civil Contingencies
OL,15,FGroup and Northern Ireland hub, we
OL,16,Fwould have done so," Sir David said.
OL,18,FBut he said, looking back now it
OL,19,Fprobably would have been prudent to
OL,20,Fhave activated the NICCMA days earlier.
