OL,7,F"Firstly, and again this is knowing
OL,8,Fwhat we know now, we didn't get the
OL,9,Fnumber of volunteers coming forward to
OL,10,Fstaff up the hub which provides
OL,11,Fsupport to CCG that we had
OL,12,Fanticipated, and for that reason it
OL,13,Fwould have been sensible I think to
OL,14,Fhave established it a little earlier
OL,15,Fso that we could have known this and
OL,16,Fmitigated."
