OL,7,FHe said there had been issues with
OL,8,Fleaks from the executive going back to
OL,9,F1998, however there is a perception it
OL,10,Fhas worsened in recent years with
OL,11,Fmobile phones with cameras now
OL,12,Fcommonplace and social media.
OL,14,FSir David said this often meant papers
OL,15,Fwere not given to ministers until the
OL,16,Flast minute, leading to adjournments
OL,17,Fto allow them to be read before
OL,18,Fmeetings.
OL,20,F"It made it harder to do business
OL,21,Fefficiently," he added.
