OL,7,FSir David also said in his experience
OL,8,Fthere was a reluctance among all of
OL,9,Fthe political parties to do things
OL,10,Fwhich they perceived would spark a
OL,11,Fnegative public reaction.
OL,13,FHowever he said when the Stormont
OL,14,Fexecutive was re-formed in January
OL,15,F2020 following three years of
OL,16,Fcollapse, he detected a "strong desire
OL,17,Famongst the new ministerial team to
OL,18,Fwork together".
