OL,7,F"I think they clearly felt that after
OL,8,Fa three-year absence they needed to
OL,9,Fstep up, they recognised that there
OL,10,Fwas a lack of public confidence in the
OL,11,Finstitutions," Sir David said, adding
OL,12,Fhe was "quite impressed by the sort of
OL,13,Fcollegiality" initially.
OL,15,FBut he said the onset of the pandemic
OL,16,Fmeant they were never able to
OL,17,Ftranslate their preliminary work into
OL,18,Fa Programme for Government.
OL,20,FSir David's evidence is due to
OL,21,Fcontinue until Wednesday evening.
