OL,8,Fthe Northern Ireland capital on
OL,9,FTuesday morning.
OL,11,FThe hearings in Belfast will run for
OL,12,Fthree weeks and are designed to
OL,13,Fprovide an opportunity to look in
OL,14,Fdepth at the decisions taken in
OL,15,FNorthern Ireland.
